A vintage 1960s-style illustration of a streamlined assembly line where colorful paper forms flow through an elegant mechanical contraption with brass gears, conveyor belts, and pneumatic tubes. The forms transform as they move through the machine—entering as blank sheets on one side and emerging on the other as neatly organized, stamped documents sliding into organized filing slots. The color palette features warm oranges, teals, and cream tones with subtle halftone dot textures. The scene has a retro-futuristic optimism, showing the machine surrounded by art deco flourishes and geometric patterns reminiscent of mid-century industrial design posters.
